<div class="title">Nice Synergy</div>
<div class="substance">2C-E & DMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Lemmiwinks&Exact=1">Lemmiwinks</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Lemmiwinks. "Nice Synergy: An Experience with 2C-E & DMT (exp61809)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 18, 2008. erowid.org/exp/61809</div>

